---
description: Data-first presentation rule
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

This project is data-first.

- Prefer dense tables, compact controls, terse labels, and direct values.
- Default to one-line rows and linear parameter layouts for operational or analytical data.
- Do not add descriptive paragraphs, explanatory subtitles, marketing copy, embellished helper text, or verbose narrative unless explicitly requested.
- When uncertain, remove words and surface the data.
